text: The NorZone Premier League is one of three top tier state-level soccer competition in the Northern Territory of Australia. It comprises teams within the NorZone region, centred in Darwin and the surrounding rural areas. The league is conducted by the state administrative body, Football Federation Northern Territory. ==Clubs== The following clubs are participating in the 2020 NorZone Premier League. * Casuarina FC * Darwin Hearts FC * Hellenic Athletic * Mindil Aces FC * Port Darwin FC * University Azzurri FC ==References== ==External links== *Football Federation Northern Territory Official website Category:Sports leagues established in 2006 Category:2006 establishments in Australia
